%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Requestor / Project Manager
participant UI as Vendor Management UI
participant BFF as Vendor BFF
participant CACHE as Redis Cache
participant VMS as Vendor Management Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}

PM ->> UI: Open Vendor Management Home
UI ->> BFF: Get requestor evaluation queue

BFF ->> CACHE: Get requestor queue cache
alt Cache Hit
    CACHE -->> BFF: Cached request list
else Cache Miss
    BFF ->> VMS: getRequestorQueue(userId, filters)
    VMS ->> READDB: GET requests, vendor <br/>count, evaluation completion status
    READDB -->> VMS: Queue records
    VMS -->> BFF: Request list with status
    BFF ->> CACHE: Cache requestor queue
end

BFF -->> UI: Display Req ID, RFQ, <br/>Project, Stage, Vendors, Status
PM ->> UI: Click Request Evaluation
UI -->> PM: Navigate to Request Evaluation form